EZ-Environment
================

*"For easy access, baby!¬† ‚Ä¶That's right.'"‚ÄîEazy-E*

Have you ever thought handling environment variables in Python should be easier?
It is now.


TL;DR:

.. code:: python

    >>> import env

    >>> env.SERVER_PORT.int
    8080

*"BAM!" ‚ÄîEmeril Lagasse*

